sessions.session_desc: COPPA ITALIA ACI ESPORT GRAN TURISMO R4 PRACTICE

Xtrememotorsports99.com Ricmotech SportsCar Series. Our Series runs every other Monday evening at 8:30pm EST. We are always seeking out interested drivers for our 2022 Season. We are looking for mature drivers that have a good attitude and conduct themselves with great sportsmanship on the track. If you would like further information and would like to join our series driver registrations will be accepted until just prior to the start of Season race 4. Visit our website @ http://www.xtrememotorsports99.com/road-series and click Register. Once you are registered, we will send you an invite through the League Portal as well as league requirements.
